doc.after: For most of its history Aeroflot s fleet consisted entirely of planes built by Soviet manufacturers Antonov Ilyushin and Tupolev Following the Soviet Union s dissolution and subsequent partition of the airline Aeroflot began replacing its old Soviet aircraft with Western and modern Russian models
